  graham.hutton@nottingham.ac.uk, by 31st August 2026:

  =E2=80=A2 Two letters of support, explaining why the dissertation should =
be
    considered for the award.  One letter should be from the
    advisor/supervisor, and one from an independent source with no
    conflict of interest with the candidate, such as an external
    examiner or other expert in the field.

  =E2=80=A2 A copy of the dissertation itself.

  AWARD COMMITTEE

  =E2=80=A2 Graham Hutton (chair), University of Nottingham
  =E2=80=A2 Matthew Flatt, University of Utah
  =E2=80=A2 Jeremy Gibbons, University of Oxford
  =E2=80=A2 Fran=C3=A7ois Pottier, INRIA
  =E2=80=A2 Wouter Swierstra, University of Utrecht
  =E2=80=A2 Ningning Xie, University of Toronto

