<h3 id=3D"orga0672b4">Fran=C3=A7ois Pottier announced</h3>
<div class=3D"outline-text-3" id=3D"text-orga0672b4">
<p>
Hello fellow users of OCaml,
If you or your students have defended a PhD in 2025 on a topic related to f=
unctional programming, then you may apply for the (new) Richard Bird Distin=
guished Dissertation Award. Announcement copied below.
